
// The Hyperlambda code retrieves the value of the [content] node, which is a child of the [message] node, itself a descendant of the root node created by the [json2lambda] slot. The [json2lambda] slot converts a JSON string into a lambda object, and the [get-value] slot fetches the specified node's value using a lambda expression.
get-value:x:@json2lambda/*/message/*/content
